m  to  she served as a member of the ici executive board from  to  and chairman of the investment committee of the ici pension fund after acting as an independent consultant to british aerospace plc from  to  she joined short brothers plc in  as executive vice president for strategy  communications she became executive vice president and general manager bombardier aerospace services uk in  in her early career she worked for bain  co and morgan stanley she has been an independent director of pepsico inc since march   she served as the chairman of the board at bbc trust since october   until january   she served as a nonexecutive director of the economist group limited since july  she has almost  years of experience in finance and global business she served as the chairman of interactive data holdings corporation from september   to july   and financial times group ltd until april  she served as an executive director of pearson plc pension arm and pearson plc from june   to april  she served as a director of financial times group limited until april  she is also a trustee director of the pearson group pension fund and has served as a non executive director of harvard business school publishing since  she served as an independent nonexecutive director of hsbc holdings plc since march   until april   she served as director of interactive data holdings corporation from february   to july   she was educated at yarm grammar school and holds a first class honors degree in law from st catharines college cambridge she was named a commander of the order of the british empire in  and was appointed as a british business ambassador in  she is a member of the united kingdom governments cabinet office supporting the prime minister to ensure effective development coordination and implantation of policy and operations across all government departments she also gained an mba from harvard business school usaread full background corporate headquarters  anderson hill roadpurchase new yor